{"tid":1350571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"寶礦力微博發岀聲明 擁護一國兩制","createTime":"2019-07-22T13:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T13:16:43.000Z","uid":105306,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"61a7c99154d7d38eb5268c32f2a426c1f687eecf","tid":1350571,"uid":105306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"聲明由寶礦力水特的母公司香港大塚製藥發出，內容表示對9日回應引起的誤解深表歉意，指「作為一家在香港經營多年的公司，我們一直支持和擁護「一國兩制」基本方針及基本法」；並「一直支持香港的穩定和繁榮」。公司將繼續竭盡所能為全世界人民健康作貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國內地寶礦力水特於7月9日在內地微博發表聲明。<br />\n反修例風波持續發酵，有網民發起抵制TVB活動，對其新聞取態表達不滿，寶礦力水特早前抽起TVB廣告，引起網民支持。中國內地寶礦力水特於7月9日在內地微博發表聲明，表示與香港寶礦力水特屬兩個完全獨立經濟過，又指擁護「一國兩制」和香港基本法，同時「堅決維護香港的繁榮穩定和長治久安，反對一切以暴力破壞社會秩序的行為」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWOWDds.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWOWDds.png&h=8949650f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: 01"},{"pid":"dc5eb853000e7abcbb79c743627413fab25f2088","tid":1350571,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjPbreK.jpg&h=068b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrX6eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKrX6eR.jpg&h=922f47ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87OcaGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87OcaGA.jpg&h=5d1b1e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買水動樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b485d52179f9fceb734e2f7297ec386d872aa3","tid":1350571,"uid":259368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:16:43.000Z","msg":"水動樂啦<br />\n太古集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}